{"tid":2312594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務院：終止五個中美交流計劃 包括涉香港教育項目","createTime":"2020-12-05T05:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T07:14:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"94a44edb82f2942cf2bad687b97f3943616471f8","tid":2312594,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"美國國務院終止五個中美交流計劃 包括涉香港教育項目<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院終止五個中美交流計劃，包括「香港教育與文化計劃」，指控這些計劃以「文化交流」之名，實際上完全由中國政府資助和營運，作為中國的軟實力政治宣傳工具，只讓中共官員參與，一般民眾則未能接觸，意味不再容許美國政府僱員，以外國政府資金參與這些項目。<br />\n<br />\n其餘被終止的計劃包括，「政策制定者中國教育旅行計劃」、「美中友誼計劃」、「美中領袖交流計劃」和「美中跨太平洋交流計劃」。美方表示，美國歡迎與中方人員和人民，作出互惠同公平的文化交流，但這些計劃只屬單向性質，並非互惠互利。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2369437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2369437&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=95202fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2369437</a>"},{"pid":"d238a87caeceee69d2edb411abcce41efcfbb3c2","tid":2312594,"uid":268591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"求撚得撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cef4100282b51b15ec404d35af9a0d1475213a5","tid":2312594,"uid":36178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊"},{"pid":"809c3780cc48f312d62cc3880c366cca45737ffe","tid":2312594,"uid":151469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4443ef09d38b684948d3a297cf04e7748aa188","tid":2312594,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"又違反國安法，呢個係基本法腐乳架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc9064dcb929bbe15ae933591ba098cc8b8eef9","tid":2312594,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,